                     <interp inst="t18451027-2042-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing 1 breast-pin, value 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 2 rings, 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; 1 sextant, 13<hi rend="italic">l</hi>.; and 3 silver coins, 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18451027-name-553" type="victimName">
