                        <interp inst="t18451027-name-560" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN COLFORD</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This sextant and one gold ring is mine—the other has not been found.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I bought the duplicate of a young man, and gave him the money to redeem the articles; he had pledged them.</p>
